               <head>Arabic and Persian grammars</head>
               <msContents class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh86000279 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2008109072">
                  <summary>Collection of works on Arabic and Persian grammar. Pencil drawings at beginning and end showing construction techniques for arches and bridges.</summary>
